dcterms:description: The dataset contains day-ahead electricity prices from the Energy Exchange Austria (EXAA), which are disclosed prior to most other European exchanges, allowing traders to incorporate this price into their calculations.
dcterms:title: EXAA (Energy Exchange Austria)

dcterms:description: The dataset includes day-ahead electricity prices from the European Power Exchange (EPEX), which operates in Germany and Austria, and is used to analyze the relationship with EXAA prices.
dcterms:title: EPEX (European Power Exchange)

dcterms:description: The dataset consists of day-ahead electricity prices from the Amsterdam Power Exchange (APX), which is analyzed in relation to the EXAA prices.
dcterms:title: APX (Amsterdam Power Exchange)

dcterms:description: The dataset includes day-ahead electricity prices from the Nordic Power Market (Nordpool), which is considered in the analysis of the impact of EXAA prices.
dcterms:title: Nordpool (Nordic Power Market)

dcterms:creator: W. Zhang
M. Zhu
K. G. Derpanis
dcterms:description: The dataset contains day-ahead electricity prices from the Polish Power Exchange (POLPX), which is used to analyze the relationship with EXAA prices.
dcterms:title: POLPX (Polish Power Exchange)

dcterms:description: The dataset includes day-ahead electricity prices from the Czech Electricity Market (OTE), which is analyzed in relation to the EXAA prices.
dcterms:title: OTE (Czech Electricity Market)

dcterms:description: The dataset consists of day-ahead electricity prices from the Hungarian Power Exchange (HUPX), which is considered in the analysis of the impact of EXAA prices.
dcterms:title: HUPX (Hungarian Power Exchange)

dcterms:description: The dataset includes day-ahead electricity prices from the Italian Power Exchange (GME), which is analyzed in relation to the EXAA prices.
dcterms:title: GME (Italian Power Exchange)

dcterms:description: The dataset consists of day-ahead electricity prices from the Slovenian Power Exchange (BSP), which is considered in the analysis of the impact of EXAA prices.
dcterms:title: BSP (Slovenian Power Exchange)
